Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.001\fs75\c&H0521D2&\3c&HEAE9C3&\4c&H38B04E&\bord5\shad8\pos(760,870)\fad(900,0)}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,30,,Did you hear about it?{Have you heard the gossip already?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:17.96,Default,,0,0,30,,Did you ever experience it?{And have you made sure yourself with those eyes?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,30,,Two shockingly beautiful eyes{/eyes - didn't wanna use the same word twice in a row, especially since in Japanese this is two different words for eyes}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,30,,A startling romance{A shockingly overflowing romance}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,30,,All-consuming{The hottest topic now}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,30,,Inescapable{It's all about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,30,,With a Taishou Era charming lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,30,,Here, here, here she is, the High Collar lady{I know you intended this to include "hai-hai-hai" but that would be obvious lie and it's evident enough without a translation what this onomatopoeia refers to - perevodildo}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,30,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over {(not really sure about what the original meaning should be)}{L-E's variant: As she spreads that kind heart - Perevodildo}{With her gentle heart, winning everyone over }
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,30,,Here, here, here she is, the High Collar lady
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,30,,Whose winning heart lavishes kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,30,,Here, here, here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,30,,Here, here, here she is, the High Collar lady
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,30,,With her gentle heart, winning everyone over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,30,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:41.52,Default,,0,0,30,,Please call me a High Collar lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:48.45,Default,,0,0,30,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.66,0:23:57.25,Default,,0,0,30,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.25,0:24:00.13,Default,,0,0,30,,to give me once again this loving glance{made up to better match song pacing}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.13,0:24:05.63,Default,,0,0,30,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have this unrequited feeling{/This unfulfilled wish is heavy}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:10.60,Default,,0,0,30,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:16.77,Default,,0,0,30,,Just a tomboyish lady with a smidgen of pretension
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.73,0:24:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1050,750)\blur1\bord0}\h Translation    alucardnoyuuutsu\h\N\h       Timing{/TLC/Lyrics}    Perevodildo         \h\NQC    Ziusudra\h
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.85,0:24:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\blur1\fs45\bord0\c&HFCF5FD&\pos(1060,500)\fs28}Brought to you by the Sorcery Party\N{\fs}ѫ~ѫ\N"Lux in Tenebris"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Taishou Era, knead with Romanticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that quiet girl is no other than Hanamura Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A High Collar lady in her\Nseventeenth year...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...But a single bamboo sword is all she needs to turn into a full-blown hoyden!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Inscrutable and interesting are the ways people are brought together...{縁は異なもの味なもの - Japanese proverb, roughly translates to "bonds are a strange and interesting thing" - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...And that's not wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As fate made her run upon a \Nprincely sublieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She challenged him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,as she wanted to test his reflexes, {I don't really understand what he's saying. I went with the Italian version.}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,only to discover that she is betrothed to him by her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde! Ten points!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twinkle twinkle little star,\Nhow I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're finally awake, Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who said that a warrior \Nshould always be vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I've never lost to anyone before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it makes me all riled up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Know-Not Fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me, I'm just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wholly cooked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you? \NCan't you see that I feel down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And that guy's supposed to be my fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.71,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,F-F-Fiancé? My future husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\c&HEAEAEA&\pos(750,400)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60.333}Episode 2\N{\fs120}Elopement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny at all when you joke about these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so you'd better stop fooling around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this is definitely not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ijuuin Shinobu is undoubtedly your husband-to-be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this is not the time to faint yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, that's so out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why on earth are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For ages, the Hanamura dynasty was a vassal family at the service of the Tokugawa Shogunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas the Ijuuin dynasty has always been a noble family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, your grandfather and Ijuuin's grandmother, who met by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,had been enamored to one other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, \Nthe night before Meiji Restoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,both were forced to break off the relationship due to the end of the Shogunate. {I added a bit of context to it  - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However, before they parted ways, they made a pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that someday, were the world becoming a better place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,their two bloodlines would intermix.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,may get split in two by a stepping stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually turn into one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In spite of that, their descent was male,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so they decided to wait until \Ntheir grandchildren's birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, I'm the chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, this is a promise that predates your births.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me! \NI flatly refuse this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a lapsed oath by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how you put it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, with a guy as him, of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to accept that this is an\Nimperishable promise between the families.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Imperial Rules states that \Nbreaking promises is a taboo. {I trusted the Italian version for some things in this section - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, they also go by this:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Warriors! Shall faithfulness be your credo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But that guy is not a warrior, he's \Na coward that takes advantage of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The same source tells something else:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"First and foremost, etiquette shall be followed".  {}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! Don't object to your father's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, very soon we'll be holding an informal wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to Ijuuin's house will get you to learn manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanny, is the bath ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I try, he won't change his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've done the right thing. \NI've always seen Benio as a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...But if I don't do anything, she'll end up increasingly more boyish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, her fiancé is from reputable nobility, so she'll learn a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,even though it might be daunting at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"That is the question."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"To be or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the question,"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure you remember that one well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a line from a work by William Shakespeare, \Na famous English man of letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura Benio, interpret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpret this line: "To be or not to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the question!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that the author is asking himself whether something is there or not. {/alternative: There is. There is not. That is a question./ This whole part is her translating this from EN to JAP so I don't know how I could put it in a better way - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing, Benio? Read this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:38.37,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2896AB&\3c&H0E3A4D&}Cheatsheet - English{トラの巻 - colloqual for cheatsheet in Japanese, literally "Tiger's book" - pere}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is suffering in life better than dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's blatantly reading the cheatsheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, should I keep on reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and get out of this class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved by the bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got defeated again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, Benio, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't English your top subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been in a daze all morning long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, to tell the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been betrothed to \Nsomeone I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he tall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a real man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you, the usual dunce, would be the first to get engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,People sure have strange tastes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme your man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he's handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like getting married yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I have interests, hopes and dreams too, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's easy for you to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she even started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't be forced to marry a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are in your good right to reject this old-fashioned marriage custom. {Not too sure about this one being 100% correct but it's something like this - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, you're the only one who understands me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,being too picky might get you to end up alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, even I, am in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Living a whole life alone is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, cheer up a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right, haven't you said that the man is a noble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, you're one too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Life in a noble family is hard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard? In which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, "Omawari", "Akaka",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Iriiri",
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okabe", "Misomiso", "Tsukutsuku", "Harihari", "Surusuru".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it short,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Omawari" stands for vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Akaka" are red beans. {/azuki beans}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,, "Iriiri" are soybeans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Okabe" means tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, "Misomiso" is miso salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harihari" stands for dried melon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,, "Tsukutsuku".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Surusuru".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it, Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these are words nobles use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't speak Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go as far,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a rather different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A world without Japanese...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I'd hate a place like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you, I got you, Tenmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumaru, good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kisaraki, is Grandmother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is currently on the terrace in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Tenmaru, Tsumaru, we'll play later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, thank you for your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandmother, yesterday\NI got to meet Lady Hanamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Then tell me, Shinobu, how did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of girl was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be full of spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say I had a good impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then would you even be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to marry that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything to make you happy, Grandmother. {not literal but sounds the best in this case - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The rapid flow of water
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,may get split in two by a stepping stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually turn into one again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, as my grandson, you're granting one of my lifetime wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is today's share of letters for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them are from women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, I've heard about your engagement, but there are still these many!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I blame them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Young Master is that handsome...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I might send in a love letter too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way back from piano classes, so I figured I'd drop by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, I'd love to hear you play sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.66,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Full of love letters as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet this amount doesn't outmatch yours. {I think there's a better phrasing for this - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.57,0:14:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you, sweet talker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Today a friend of mine got betrothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of it, her fiancé is a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he's like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I'll be as lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but isn't it easier to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,given all the proposals you get every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is too different from my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:32.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H50443F&\3c&HCAC6B9&}Garden of Flowers{It says literally "garden flower life" but I guess some flower shop will do - pere}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These safflowers are a rare sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they'd match her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you send the flowers to this address?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing! Oh, are these a gift for your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok then, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but by acting this carelessly, your reputation will drop down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He really hasn't greeted my feelings at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since the times we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Spring, and yet it's still so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady, the dinner is ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Grilled chicken, your favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been her favourite dish, but she isn't even opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A hunger strike,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and she seems determined about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But she'll certainly feel ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if she keeps on going like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe we shouldn't hastily judge it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,girls who are betrothed usually start to self reflect,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This book is so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H131679&\3c&H476E9C&}Here Comes the High Collar Lady
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,King, King, Ki-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,not funny anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do, I keep feeling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even feel like practising fencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the quiet spectacle of snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, what are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get near the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you stay outside like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, it's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrothed... Betrothed that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,always liked you, ever since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but my social status is lower, and I'm one year younger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I've never told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's my dad's decision and I can't go against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, according to what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that second lieutenant seems to be a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But to make such a decision all of a sudden when there is so much I'd like to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, what the Dickens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd lose everything just to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even Kabuki as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:20:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that, I like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a brotherly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's ok, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's meet tonight, I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell me something like that, \Nhe went all this way through the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is all of this happening all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ranmaru is cute, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I feel like I can't just ignore him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but running away with him? That's a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be ill advised to do a drastic thing like elope...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.77,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shakespeare said:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is suffering in life better than dying? \NThat is the dilemma."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've received flowers from Sublieutenant Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,These are safflowers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He even attached a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not a color
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very fond of..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a color I'm very fond of, but, for some reason,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still picked these safflowers for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not a color I'm very fond of,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so, if I had to interpret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I he doesn't have deep feelings about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,he still decided to send these safflowers with some kind of intention, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Safflowers, typically used as a dye... {Here she makes a pun with 紅花 (紅 meaning red/crimson and 花(flower) having the same reading as 鼻(nose)), so I had to change it in some way for it to make sense / she also makes a joke with Benio, her name, and Benibana - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers meant for dyeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So he meant to dye my nose red!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is coming together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he could be this mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never liked him, but now I'm completely done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than marry such a guy, I may as well run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can dare make fun at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ranmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye Dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,home, friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and fiancé, I'll be walking on my own from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, walking at a fast pace alongside Ranmaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Benio is determined to start anew.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Escaping from the forceful engagement and live the "High Collar" way. Where will they go? {This is not very precise as it's hard to get all of what he's saying. It should be close, though. - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,High Collar Benio is running away with Ranmaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:22:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,following the path of true love,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,might lead to unexpected encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As Ushigorou from the Kurumahiki clan, \Nwilling to become a girl's escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything will turn into a cheerful bender and a drunken singalong, {He's talking about 嗚呼玉杯に花うけて, a Japanese dormitory song}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,only to meet her blond \Nsublieutenant fiancé once again. {Like the episode narrator conclusion, this is somewhat approximate - Alucard}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Here Comes the High Collar Lady:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.46,0:23:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A romantic hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
